snippet.textDisplay:
Okay, I am actually digging this a lot 😍 some suggestions tho:
It would be cool if you added more ruffles to the shirt, you know? Kind of having a Victorian-esque vibe but also like a full on glam too. More ruffles would add drama to the shirt (and we looove drama). Also maybe mixing the glittery fabric and the see through white fabric could help the shirt look more together. (Also, you need some lining at the sleeves, even though people won’t see them. Or maybe add glittery sleeves).

Now, the jacket... I looooove it. But what if you add like a puffy sleeve with a little bit of a fringe? We loooove a puffy sleeve moment.

Overall, I am so happy and so amazed at your talent! I am so happy about your wedding guys :’) <3 lots of love!❤️
